/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得益都只會係班做倫敦金既狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e1030100ed17c1d8a7b832b301060e793883298","tid":117693,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T13:18:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>至少好過做倫敦金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n保險都叫真係有機會用得著</blockquote><br />\n兩位巴打做保險架？</blockquote><br />\n真心覺得，保險有時真係幫到人，係有啲人眼光狹窄，放左係比保險狗呃，一碌鳩打一船人姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反而倫敦金只係聽過比人呃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得益都只會係班做倫敦金既狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我諗個問題係唔點洗讀書但人工可以好高"},{"pid":"13f1e24211ec70975734f1f51826d0e478744224","tid":117693,"uid":3577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T13:24:22.000Z","msg":"幫到人, 自己又開心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77ddf3b6593473792ff77a17f6c5ae7ffcf540c7","tid":117693,"uid":3735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T13:52:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>至少好過做倫敦金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n保險都叫真係有機會用得著</blockquote><br />\n兩位巴打做保險架？</blockquote><br />\n真心覺得，保險有時真係幫到人，係有啲人眼光狹窄，放左係比保險狗呃，一碌鳩打一船人姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反而倫敦金只係聽過比人呃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得益都只會係班做倫敦金既狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我諗個問題係唔點洗讀書但人工可以好高</blockquote><br />\n你有客就係囉 好似呢條友咁 有父幹 識得人多 daddy又射d客比佢 咪fat fat 自己出黎做個細既經紀仔咪又係發唔到圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ead57bc110ccbc5bfb5c6b1ad5c01550632d25e6","tid":117693,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T13:55:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.metrohkhub.info/media/2014/news/2014-06-08/2014060823230906.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.metrohkhub.info%2Fmedia%2F2014%2Fnews%2F2014-06-08%2F2014060823230906.jpg&h=0cc918a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲信奉基督教的Solomon，態度正面積極，常存感恩的心。"},{"pid":"8910b93dc873845f5fb0dae992c821030b3a42b8","tid":117693,"uid":73492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T13:56:23.000Z","msg":"老豆，教會同隊波比佢抽水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7555632bcac4823a27520dad81c1935da52212b9","tid":117693,"uid":7343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T14:00:58.000Z","msg":"TOT<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 堅勁"},{"pid":"a2586f2dcf9b1441b6b6b86a3ad7a289137fbff3","tid":117693,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T14:14:25.000Z","msg":"我之前買左保險，入私院治療同檢查真係保到足<br />\n所以我好慶幸買左。<br />\n我個人認為身在香港係真係有需要買醫療保險，<br />\n而份保險一定要保到會係私家做檢查，<br />\n自己睇清楚份保既條文<br />\n唔係既話排公家可能到死都未檢查到。<br />\n<br />\n可能連登仔或者高登仔好反感保險，<br />\n但我自己覺得d19類型既保險可以睬佢都笨柒，<br />\n不過醫療類同旅遊類係真心要買（尤其係窮撚）<br />\n最多望清望楚，問多兩句"},{"pid":"f825cdb2c337b2c7023939405b13654178809515","tid":117693,"uid":1790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T14:20:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://static.metrohkhub.info/media/2014/news/2014-06-08/2014060823230906.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.metrohkhub.info%2Fmedia%2F2014%2Fnews%2F2014-06-08%2F2014060823230906.jpg&h=0cc918a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲信奉基督教的Solomon，態度正面積極，常存感恩的心。</blockquote><br />\n投胎投得好 緊係感恩啦"}]}